    <item>
      <title>You Will Live a Meaningful Life, If You Follow Me</title>
      <link>https://laluneelevee.github.io/chatstory/20201229_you-will-live-a-meaningful-life_if-you-follow-me/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://laluneelevee.github.io/chatstory/20201229_you-will-live-a-meaningful-life_if-you-follow-me/</guid>
      <description>Yuta: What do you think a meaningful life? Momi: I can&amp;rsquo;t give you a clear answer. Momi: Do you want to live a meaningful life? Yuta: Sure. Momi: For what? Yuta: I don&amp;rsquo;t know. Momi: For whom? Yuta: For me? Momi: That is the most important thing. Momi: Because a meaning varies on the person. Momi: Only humans can understand the meanings. Momi: So, you need a meaning of life. Momi: Don&amp;rsquo;t you?</description>
